title: Don't Trend It All In One Place 7/22: Alaska Earthquake, iPod, Donald Glover, NBA Bubble
itunes:title: Don't Trend It All In One Place 7/22: Alaska Earthquake, iPod, Donald Glover, NBA Bubble
description:
On this edition of Don't Trend It All In One Place Jack and Miles discuss the 7.8 earthquake in Alaska that set off tsunami warnings, people are remembering the many forms of the iPod for whatever reason, Donald Glover is going to star in a Lando Disney+ series, and the boys discuss the state of the NBA Bubble.
